snippet.title: Tony Evans
snippet.description:
Could you use a bit more hope? We know. Life can be hard. You need a place where you can find wholeness again. Happiness. Even strength. That’s why we’re here. Walking with you on this journey to your destiny. Whether it’s a short video devotional for those moments when you are waiting to pick up the kids or have just a few minutes before you are about to fall asleep, or whether it’s a full length sermon to sharpen your spiritual tools - we’ve put our best on here to help you be your best everywhere.

Tony Evans guides millions into greater spiritual wholeness through his messages. As a pastor and author, his joy comes through witnessing others enjoy God's Word and presence like never before. An easy way to listen to his daily sermons is on his free app, which you can download in the App Store. Just search for Tony Evans.

tonyevans.org
